				<td colspan="2"><span>In UP the skeletons that drop the druid armor do not summon.  They aren't worth a lot of exp though.  You can round up a decent pack, and swarm them down.  If you get a summoner in the pack, charm burn it.  Avoid the robe guys, fade off em, and you should be fine. 
<br />

<br />
The named one for that type does summon, but you can kill him anyway, just keep throwing charmed critters at him. 
<br />

<br />
Also, in PoN, with a combo of selo, levitate, DA and fade you can run through the mephit caves to the plateau.  You can kill the nightmares up there (so I'm told) or you can hang out in the mephit cave and kill them.  The mephits are good for cash drops, or tradeskill items (nightmare mephit blood).  But some of the mephits cast, so there's a learning curve.  </span></td>
