				<td colspan="2"><span>Note on the Elysians:
<br />

<br />
They cast Root, which occasionaly will stick.  They charm with the 64 version quite easily.  Path here really stink though, so be prepard to pull over the hill, and then wait for a while.
<br />

<br />
Nice drops here, even if you aren't a Druid.  If you don't have a Druid alt, or friend to bring along, there are better places for XP though.</span></td>
